Package: wfprogression
Title: Processing and analysis of fire spread data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Michael", "Storey", , "mstorey@uow.edu.au", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6662-9192"))
Description: The package has functions that take a fire polygon and finds
    all the intersecting remote sensing data that may be used to measure
    the fires rate of spread.  This includes line scans from a database,
    Landsat and Sentinel imagery and MODIS and VIIRS imagery.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
